Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.60,0:00:07.53,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Like an angel that has no\Nsense of mercy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.53,0:00:14.53,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Rise, young boy, to the heavens\Nlike a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:26.42,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Cold winds, as blue as the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:30.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Tear open the door to\Nyour heart, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:33.80,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,But unknowing you seem, just\Nstaring at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:38.14,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Standing there smiling serenely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:41.27,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Desperate, for something to touch...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:45.06,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,A moment of kindness like\Nthat in a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:48.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Your innocent eyes, have yet no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:51.90,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Of the path your destiny will follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:56.20,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,But someday you’ll become aware of...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:00:58.91,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Everything that you’ve got behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:03.83,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Your wings are for seeking out a new...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:06.75,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Future that only you can search for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:14.93,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,The cruel angel’s thesis enters through\Nthe window of your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.93,0:01:18.72,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,If you should betray the chapel\Nof your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:22.39,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,The cruel angel’s thesis bleeds through\Na portal like your pulsing blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:26.10,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,So, boy, stand tall and embrace\Nthe fire of the legend,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:30.20,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Embracing the universe like\Na blazing star!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:36.44,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hi!  I’m not in right now,\Nso leave your message after the beep!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:42.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This may be my last assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:45.71,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This looks like blood.
