Dialogue: 5,0:01:48.94,0:01:51.44,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Text,The Vice-Commander was abducted?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.44,0:01:56.71,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Two hours ago.\NHe was last seen in the 8th District.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.71,0:01:58.58,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s inside our installation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:02:00.88,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What in the hell were you idiots\Nin Intelligence doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:04.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The whole thing was set up by someone\Ninside our operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.09,0:02:06.15,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We were taken by surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:09.66,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Someone who could outwit Section 2?\NIt couldn’t be him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:14.33,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ryoji Kaji is suspected of being the\Nmastermind behind this plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.33,0:02:16.83,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Then, that’s why you came for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:18.97,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We believe that you can\Nbe of use to us, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:24.07,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,As your colleagues,\Nwe regret having to consider\Nthe Director of Operations a suspect...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.07,0:02:26.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...but that is the nature of our profession.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.11,0:02:30.28,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Considering our relationship,\Nit’s a natural precaution.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:31.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I appreciate your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.98,0:02:33.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Take her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:38.96,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s been a while, Chairman Keel.\NThis is a rather rough reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:42.03,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I will not apologize\Nfor necessary discourtesies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.69,0:02:46.40,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This was necessary in order for us\Nto speak with you outside of the\NCommander’s presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:50.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You haven’t changed.  You still have no\Nconcern for the circumstances of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:55.24,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The subject to be addressed\Nhas become an immediate concern.\NThus, these measures were unavoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:57.07,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Please understand our situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:03:00.31,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What a surprise.\NNot the committee, but SEELE itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:03.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We have no intention of\Ncreating a new god.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:06.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We hope that we will have your\Ncooperation, Professor Fuyutsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:10.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}Professor Fuyutsuki, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:13.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Professor!  Professor Fuyutsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:16.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hello, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:19.39,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why don’t you join us for a beer\Nby the Kamo River?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.39,0:03:20.60,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:24.20,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ryoko and the other girls said\Nthey’ll come if you come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:26.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The professor said that you shouldn’t\Nbe so unsociable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:28.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,All right, I’ll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:33.14,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s nice to have a drink outside\Nfor a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:34.24,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:39.41,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re very competent,\Nbut you tend to underestimate\Nthe value of relationships with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:40.75,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:42.72,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, Fuyutsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:47.52,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...there’s a student who wrote\Na very interesting research paper\Nfor the bio-engineering class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:50.56,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Her name is Ikari.  Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:52.99,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ikari?  No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.99,0:03:56.67,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ve told her about you,\Nand she says she’d like to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:04:00.04,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,She’ll be calling you soon,\Nand I’d like you to take her on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:02.41,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And her name is Ikari?  I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:06.51,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ve read your paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:10.15,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,There are a few things I disagree with,\Nbut it’s really very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:11.58,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:13.95,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Your name is Yui Ikari, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:15.15,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:18.25,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What are your career plans?\NCorporate research?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:21.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Or joining the school research facility?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:23.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I haven’t really thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:26.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And there may be a third option.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:30.70,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m also thinking about getting married...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:32.91,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...assuming that I meet the right person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:39.84,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,By incorporating the S2 unit into itself,\Nit has achieved its ultimate form.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:42.01,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Evangelion Unit 01!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:45.51,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A supreme being which we created.\NWhat blasphemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.75,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The creation of a god is unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:51.35,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Man must not create gods.  We cannot\Nallow him to possess such power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:54.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Can we trust Gendo Ikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:58.53,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Gendo Rokubungi?\NWell, I have heard the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:01.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, I’ve never met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:04.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,However, he does seem to be\Nat the center of many rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:08.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,He wants to be released into my custody?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:12.18,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, I’ll come visit him.\NWhat time should I come?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:18.82,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ve been hearing some interesting things\Nabout you.  I’ve been wanting to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:23.29,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You were drunk and got into a fight.\NHow pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:26.39,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I didn’t even have a chance to say\Nanything before they jumped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:30.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m not used to being liked.  Being hated,\Non the other hand, is quite familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:34.93,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s not my concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:39.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Professor Fuyutsuki, you are exactly the\Nkind of person I expected you to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:44.51,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,My first impression of him was that\Nhe was a total son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:49.45,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Back then, there were still seasons\Nin this country.  It was autumn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:51.18,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:54.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, I’m dating Mr. Rokubungi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:58.69,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,When she told me that,\NI couldn’t hide my shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:02.96,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s hard to imagine you walking with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:04.93,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Now, Professor Fuyutsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:07.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...he’s actually a very sweet person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:09.80,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s just that nobody really knows him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:12.80,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Sometimes ignorance can be bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:15.90,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m the one who first mentioned you\Nto him.  Does that bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:20.62,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, I’ll admit that he’s an interesting\Nfellow, but I just don’t like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:26.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Actually, it was generally believed that the\Nreal object of his overtures to Yui...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:29.82,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...was her talent and the support of the\Norganization that was backing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:34.60,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,According to the rumors,\Nthat organization was called SEELE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:38.19,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Second Impact...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:41.70,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...it was in the last year of the 20th century\Nthat this tragedy occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:46.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Then, in the first year of the 21st century\Nthere was nothing but hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:48.71,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I can’t find any other words\Nto describe that year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.67,0:06:55.71,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This used to be a continent of ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:57.05,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,There’s no sign left of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:06:59.05,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Professor Fuyutsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:02.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is that you?  You survived?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:07.06,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’d heard that you were with the\NKatsuragi research team.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:11.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Fortunately, I returned to Japan\Nthe day before the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:13.60,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You don’t say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:14.90,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Mr. Rokubungi, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:17.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but I’ve changed my surname.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:21.67,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A postcard?  Not a business card?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:26.24,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ikari!  Gendo Ikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:31.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,My wife’s been asking me to send this to\Nyou.  She says she’s a fan of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:33.25,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:37.65,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,How is Yui doing?\NShe’s not participating in this expedition?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:41.33,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yui wanted to come too,\Nbut we have a child now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:48.40,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Your organization, SEELE or whatever it’s\Ncalled, is at the root of many ugly rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:51.38,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t like the way that it manipulates\Nthe committee by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:53.87,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re still too scrupulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:57.27,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No completely chaste organization\Ncan survive in this day and age.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:08:05.22,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,If this official investigation of the Second\NImpact was composed solely of SEELE\Npersonnel, there would have been trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:08.46,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,So, are we just here for\Npolitical convenience?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:18.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}I still hate the darkness.  All it does is\Nbring back the most horrible memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:20.70,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:23.20,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The only survivor of the research team.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:26.47,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Her name is Misato Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:29.57,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Katsuragi?\NIs she Doctor Katsuragi’s daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:33.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, she hasn’t said a word in two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.41,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,How terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:36.51,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,She saw hell firsthand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:40.82,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Her physical wounds are healed,\Nbut repairing the damage to\Nher mind will take time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:43.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.49,0:08:46.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The results of our investigation\Naren’t easy to analyze.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:49.72,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The origin of this Giant of Light is but one\Nof many mysteries we have yet to solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:56.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Second Impact was caused\Nby a massive meteorite strike, or so\Nthe United Nations officially declared later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:08:59.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,However, from my point of view...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:02.70,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...the announcement was obviously\Na fabrication.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:07.39,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The organization known as SEELE and a\Nman named Keel were behind this artifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:11.52,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It became my goal to find\Nout the truth about the incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:15.62,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...even though I discovered that\NYui Ikari was involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:19.69,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why did you conceal the\Nexistence of the Giant?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:25.96,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You knew that the Second Impact was\Ngoing to happen, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:31.64,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You may have said that it was just\Nluck that you returned the day\Nbefore it happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:35.91,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...but how do you explain the fact that you\Nbrought back copies of all\Nthe documentation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.04,0:09:41.35,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m surprised that those weren’t destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:44.79,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ve checked into your finances as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.51,0:09:50.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Bringing up a child and educating him is\Nexpensive, but isn’t this a bit much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:55.66,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Very impressive, Professor Fuyutsuki.\NPerhaps you should be teaching\Neconomics.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:10:00.93,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m going to go public with the real\Ntruth about the Second Impact, about you,\NSEELE and the Dead Sea Scrolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:04.47,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I can’t forgive anyone who would have\Ncaused something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:05.90,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:08.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,However, before you do that,\Nthere’s something I’d like to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:13.04,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’re getting rather far down, aren’t we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:14.61,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:16.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.15,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:22.52,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We didn’t create it,\Nsomeone else excavated this cavity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:25.29,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,89% of its total volume is buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:27.86,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Was this originally a giant sphere?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:32.84,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This facility is what has been consuming\Nthe total resources of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:41.47,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hi, Professor Fuyutsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:44.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Doctor Akagi, you’re here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:49.91,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, this is the ideal place for\Nour research into creating a functioning\Nbio-computer system.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:53.88,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m going to name them the “MAGI.”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:57.39,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,“MAGI”?  The three wise men of the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.39,0:10:59.39,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is this what you wanted to show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.39,0:11:01.99,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, it’s over this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:03.70,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ritsuko, I’ll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:08.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:10.33,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This can’t be THE Giant?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:13.70,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, here at Gehirn,\Nwe refer to that giant as “Adam”...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:17.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...but this isn’t the original one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:19.31,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Then, this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:23.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...was created from Adam by man, Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:24.71,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:30.69,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Our operation to revive Adam is referred\Nto as Project E.  This is Eva Unit 00,\Nour system prototype.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is a prototype of a god!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.59,0:11:38.44,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Fuyutsuki, let us create a new genesis\Nfor mankind, together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:51.41,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:55.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.  Let’s proceed with Rei’s re-test.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:57.35,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Where is Major Katsuragi today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:12:00.01,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:01.15,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Miss Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.69,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, Misato Katsuragi,\Npleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.02,0:12:08.69,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Mother, I have just become acquainted\Nwith a girl named Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:11.96,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Most people tend to keep their distance\Nfrom me once they find out who I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:15.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...which forces me to remember how\Nimportant your name is around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:19.34,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,However, Misato is different.\NShe’s very open and honest, even with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:24.14,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ve heard that she is the only survivor of\Nthe original research team...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:26.31,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...and that she was once mute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.31,0:12:30.28,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,She talks quite a lot now, almost as if\Nshe’s trying to make up for lost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.15,0:12:34.96,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Dear Ritsuko,\NI’m always underground these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:38.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...and I’m getting sick of living on the\Nbox lunches they provide here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:43.26,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,On the surface, they’ve started\Nconstruction of Tokyo-3, as directed\Nby the Second Capitol Transfer Directive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:49.83,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Misato didn’t show up for classes the last\Nfew days, and I finally forced her to tell\Nme why.  Talk about stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:55.55,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,She’d spent the whole week having\Nnon-stop sex with her new boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:58.67,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I think there’s another side to her\NI haven’t seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:01.41,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,She introduced me to him today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:05.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,He’s handsome,\Nbut his unkempt manner bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:10.18,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’ve always been a little\Nboy-shy, Ritsuko dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:12.69,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I think it’s because you only had a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:16.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And I’m afraid I didn’t take\Ncare of you properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:19.86,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m ashamed to admit that I only acted like\Na mother when it suited my whims.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:23.06,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Like a mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:32.41,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why is there a child in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:34.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s Director Ikari’s son.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:39.15,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ikari, this is not a day-care center.\NThis is a very important day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:42.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, Professor.  I brought him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:45.85,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yui, this is your experiment today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:50.79,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s why I brought him.  I want to show\Nhim how bright the future will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:53.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Those words would be Yui’s last.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:57.34,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A freak accident wiped her\Nfrom this existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:14:01.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Just as I had hoped it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:03.67,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What a disgusting woman I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:08.21,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ritsuko, after that day, Director Ikari\Ncompletely changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:11.58,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Where have you been all week?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:12.85,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I understand your grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:16.95,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...but you must be aware of your\Nown importance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:22.06,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I know.  Fuyutsuki, as of today we\Nwill begin the new project.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:24.99,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I have already made the proposal\Nto Chairman Keel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:26.79,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re really going to do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:31.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, that which has never been achieved\Nbefore, the path to becoming a god!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:33.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Human Instrumentality Project.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:38.84,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Mother, congratulations on completing\Nyour “MAGI” theorems.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:41.04,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I have good news which I think\Nwill please you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:44.41,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I have been officially accepted by Gehirn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:47.22,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ll start working on Project E next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:54.16,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:59.33,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Technology Development Section,\NRitsuko Akagi.  Here’s my ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:03.93,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I heard that the basic installation of\Nthe Command Center had been completed,\Nso I came to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:05.63,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But it’s a real maze down here, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:09.41,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Director and Doctor Akagi will\Nsee you in the Command Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:13.37,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are you really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:16.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, I have no regrets about my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:19.52,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re lying!  You still can’t forget\Nabout Yui, can you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:23.69,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But that’s acceptable to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:41.01,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s Gehirn Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:45.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Good morning, Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:46.81,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Did you bring your child?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:49.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, I thought you had a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:53.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This isn’t Shinji.  I’ve decided to take\Ncare of an acquaintance’s child.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:55.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Her name is Rei Ayanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:57.62,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,How are you, Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.32,0:16:01.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In,{\fad(170,0)}She resembles someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:04.83,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade Out,{\fad(0,170)}Yui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:08.53,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,All of the records concerning Rei Ayanami\Nhave been deleted?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:10.26,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,They’re all blank!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:10.26,0:16:11.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Text,What’s going on here?
