Dialogue: 3,0:16:11.19,0:16:13.66,Title (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Text,{\blur0.7)}{\pos(360,206)}System
Dialogue: 4,0:16:11.19,0:16:13.66,Title (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Text,{\blur0.7)}{\pos(360,330)}Complete
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:14.90,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,MAGI Casper...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.90,0:16:16.57,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,MAGI Balthasar...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:18.02,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,MAGI Melchior...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:20.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The MAGI are the three aspects of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:26.02,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Myself as a scientist, myself as a mother\Nand myself as a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:28.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Those three aspects are in constant\Nconflict with one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:30.35,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Three mothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:33.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The only thing left to do\Nis to switch the power on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.46,0:16:38.89,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ll be taking off early today.\NMisato just got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:42.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard that she joined Gehirn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:43.40,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,In Germany, if I remember correctly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:45.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, she’s stationed with the 3rd Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:48.07,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,So, she’s having a\Nlong-distance relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:49.44,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,They broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:52.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, but they seemed like\Nsuch a perfect couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:54.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The things that happen between men and\Nwomen are hard to comprehend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:56.34,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,They’re not logical.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:59.41,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re always so cold about these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:02.16,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You may lose your chance at happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:05.56,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The definition of happiness is\Neven harder to fathom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:09.16,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, I can’t wait to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:10.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:11.86,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A good time it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:27.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What’s the matter, Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:28.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:32.38,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is that so?\NDo you want to come with me then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:34.58,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:37.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But how will you get home by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:39.29,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s none of your business, old hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.76,0:17:41.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:44.60,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I can get home by myself.\NLeave me alone, old hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:48.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You shouldn’t call someone a hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.43,0:17:50.67,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But you are an old hag, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:54.37,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m getting angry.\NDirector Ikari will spank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:57.27,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Director is the one\Nwho calls you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.27,0:17:57.91,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:18:01.55,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,“That old hag is annoying.\NThat old hag is no use anymore.”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:05.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,“That old hag is annoying.\NThat old hag is no use anymore.”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:07.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...old hag...  old hag...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:10.85,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,“That old hag is annoying.\NThat old hag is no use anymore.”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:11.75,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Director said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:13.65,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...that old hag is annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:17.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...no use...  no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:24.64,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In,{\fad(170,0)}You little bitch!  Did you know you’re\Nreplaceable, too, Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:27.51,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade Out,{\fad(0,170)}Replaceable just like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:39.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Keel Lorenz, chairman of the\NInstrumentality Committee...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:43.12,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...dissolved the Gehirn Research\NOrganization immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:47.66,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,In order to complete the project, the\Nspecial organization “NERV” was formed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:51.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We all transferred to NERV,\Nexcept for one person...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:56.81,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...the one who had rendered\Nsuch remarkable service to the\NMAGI System, Dr. Akagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:04.24,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, it’s you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:05.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:08.58,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s been a while.  The guards are sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:12.21,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This action could result in your death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:14.22,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,All I want is to get closer to the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:16.38,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...to have it in my grasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:20.86,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:23.52,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:26.40,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, the problem has been solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:29.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:31.63,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:33.14,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:48.35,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, hi!  You’re a little late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:55.19,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:38.90,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Katsuragi, it’s me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:43.61,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m sure you’re listening to this message,\Nespecially after I caused you\Nso much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:45.67,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:47.85,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Please tell Ritsuko “I’m sorry,” too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:53.31,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And there’s one more thing to trouble you\Nwith.  I’ve been growing melons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:55.82,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’d appreciate it if you could\Nwater them for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.82,0:20:58.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji knows where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:05.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Katsuragi, the truth is with you.\NDon’t hesitate, move ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.63,0:21:10.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,If I ever see you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:12.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...I’ll say the words that I couldn’t\Nsay eight years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:14.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.74,0:21:17.34,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This message was recorded at 12:02 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:22.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:26.02,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You were always such a fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:52.57,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,All I could do was run away from the\Ntragedy Misato was facing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.61,0:21:55.81,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,There was nothing I could say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:21:57.91,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I was just a child...
Dialogue: 3,0:21:59.38,0:22:00.88,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Text,...but I understood.
