Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.96,0:23:21.33,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...and the damage inflicted in the next\NAngel’s attack is even more horrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,0:23:24.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji can find no words to soothe\Nher shattered soul.
